        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Accelerated Payments for Small Businesses Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a goal for federal agencies to pay small business invoices within 15 days of receiving a proper invoice if a specific payment date is not established by contract.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
